HEADWORD: Subperiosteal
<hw>Sub*per`i*os"te*al</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<fld>(Anat.)</fld> <def>Situated under the periosteum.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Subperiosteal operation</b></col> <fld>(Surg.)</fld>,
<cd>a removal of bone effected without taking away the
periosteum.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Subperitoneal</ent>⟦br⟧
